Rip notes: Nothing Was Ripped

Powerstone 2 presents you with more of everything. More gameplay modes, more playable characters, more stages &
multi-player mayhem (now up to 4 players). Escape from the clutches of Dr Erode and his minions through 3D arenas, fighting with your hands & feet or with the huge amount of weapons at your disposal. Along the way you'll encounter Boss characters to test
your fighting skills the limit. So what you waiting for Lets kick some butt ....